beIN SPORTS 1.title_en: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_ar: Paris SG and Newcastle’s only previous meetings came in the 2023-24 UEFA Champions League – the two sides drew their meeting at the Parc des Princes, after Eddie Howe’s side had won 4-1 in the first game at St. James’ Park. This will be Newcastle’s 10th away game against a French side in Europe, while they have only managed one victory from the previous nine : 4-0 v Sochaux in the UEFA Cup in November 2004.
